          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Excitation function of the U-235 fission cross-section",
                "in the energy range 0.017 eV to 0.15 eV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "EXP-YEAR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                1972
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "REAC"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " VVR-S reactor at Bucharest"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Time of flight.",
                " For each energy group of neutrons, the ratio",
                " n-fis(E)/n-gam(E) was determined, where=",
                "  .N-fis(E) is the number of events detected by the",
                "     fission chamber,",
                "  .N-gam(E) is the number of events detected by the NaI",
                "     spectrometer which counted the 447.4 keV gamma",
                "     rays of Li-7 (from B-10(n,alfa)Li-7).",
                " The fission cross-section sig(E) for each energy group",
                " was determined using the following relation=",
                "sig(E) = sig(0)*(n-fis(E)/n-gam(E))/(n-fis(0)/n-gam(0))",
                " where sig(0), n-fis(0) and n-gam(0) are the values at",
                " 2200 m/sec."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FISCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Fission chamber"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Na-I spectrometer"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
